# Using the style guide API

Components ready to use via our [style guide API](https://github.com/hagenburger/styleguide-api). To use the API, add this to your _Gemfile:_

``` ruby
gem "styleguide-api"
```

And activate the API in Middlemanâ€™s _config.rb:_

@import components-middleman-config.erb

After restarting Middleman, the templates are available as shown in the examples below.

@css
  background: $white
  display: block
  padding: 100px 0
